enb_long_title: Ninth Conference of the Parties to the UN Framework Convention on Climate Change
sentences: SBI addressed two issues under this agenda item.
On Tuesday, 2 December, Parties discussed a proposal by Belarus to use 1990 as its base-year.
The EU said only the COP/MOP has authority to decide on the issue.
Chair Stoycheva said she would prepare draft conclusions on the issue.
On Tuesday, 9 December, Chair Stoycheva introduced draft conclusions on this matter, which were adopted.
